   Elsewhere in television ....
</P>
<P>
   GLORIOUS GLORIA: Gloria Reuben, memorable as nurse Jeanie Boulet
on ''ER,'' has made herself over as a backup singer for Tina
Turner. Her transformation is detailed in ''VH1 Rock &AMP; Roll
Fantasy: Gloria Reuben,'' which follows her through her stage debut
with Turner at this year's Super Bowl pre-game show and rehearsals
for what Turner has billed as a farewell tour. The show debuts
10:30 p.m. Eastern Friday (July 7).
</P>
