<HEADLINE> Frey wins Swedish Hill Winery stake  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	   LAKE PLACID, N.Y. (AP) - Kimberly Frey of Middleburg, Va., won
the Swedish Hill Winery Speed Stake Thursday at the 23rd annual I
Love New York Horse Show in Lake Placid.
</P>
<P>
   Frey was the third of 37 entrants to try the 13-jump, one-round
course at the North Elba Show Grounds. She rode Samoens to a time
of 53.933 seconds without penalty to take an early lead.
</P>
