   Five rides later, McLain Ward of Brewster beat Frey's time,
finishing in 51.238 seconds on 4 Seasons. A rail down at the third
fence, however, added four penalties to his time, moving him to
third place.
</P>
<P>
   Christopher Cawley of Keswick, Va., rode Darling Star to a time
of 54.239 seconds to finish in second place.
</P>
<P>
   The show continues through Sunday.
