<HEADLINE> General Challenge Draws No. 7 Slot  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   INGLEWOOD, Calif. (AP) -- General Challenge, the early 9-5
favorite for Sunday's $1 million Gold Cup at Hollywood Park, drew
the No. 7 post position Thursday.
</P>
<P>
   That slot has been lucky, with the most Gold Cup winners -- 13 --
