David, Pleasant Breeze and Early Pioneer in the next three spots.
Chester House will start from the No. 5 slot, with Big Ten at No.
6. Flanking General Challenge to the outside will be Blueprint and
Out Of Mind, the 5-2 second choice in the early line.
