returning to the Governor's Mansion when staffers jumped out yelling,
''surprise'' on his 54th birthday. About 300 workers from Bush's office and
presidential campaign threw him a party on the lawn, singing ''Happy Birthday.''
''Aw thanks, we all have one,'' Bush said earlier.
